verses.text:
And he said unto them, Tell me now, ye sons of Chanaan, who this people is, that dwelleth in the hill country, and what
are the cities that they inhabit, and what is the multitude of their army, and wherein is their power and strength, and what
king is set over them, or captain of their army;

Now when she heard the evil words of the people against the governor, that they fainted for lack of water; for Judith had
heard all the words that Ozias had spoken unto them, and that he had sworn to deliver the city unto the Assyrians after five
days;
